    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a lash of lightning energy that strikes at one creature of your choice that you can see within 15 feet of you. The target must succeed on a Strength saving throw or be pulled up to 10 feet in a straight line toward you and then take 1d8 lightning damage if it is within 5 feet of you.</p><p>This spell's range and pull distance are increased by an additional 5 feet and damage increases by 1d8 when you reach 5th level (2d8), range and pull distance are increased by an additional 5 feet and 11th level (3d8), range and pull distance are increased by an additional 5 feet and and 17th level (4d8).</p>",
